moonlighting debuted in the spring of 1985 as a midseason 
replacement it rejuvenated cybill shepherds career and made an 
instant star of bruce willis 
audiences were wowed by the chemistry and sexual tension between 
shepherds maddie hayes a straightlaced former model whose 
