dont tell a soul sire the replacements 
 
the replacements gradual switch from a raucous punk sound to a 
more mature melodic rock has drawn plenty of complaints from old 
fans who snipe that theyre selling out 
its all rather silly 
if the musics good it will find an audience but in this case 
the audience wont be terribly large dont tell a soul isnt a 
