<TEXT>
composer gian carlo menotti will direct his 
first mozart opera in the united states at this years spoleto 
festival 
the marriage of figaro is already sold out for seven 
performances at the spoleto festival usa in charleston sc 
which runs may 26 through june 11 
however in an interview before leaving for the 13th annual 
festival menotti was more enthusiastic about performances by the 
colla family marionettes 
when i was a child in milan there was a small theater a 
replica of la scala for the colla puppets he said all 
children from milan were dying to go see them on sundays they had 
ballets some were replicas of the 1890s very small 
then they were just forgotten except by gian carlo when i 
started the festival in spoleto italy in 1958 i made an 
investigation about the colla puppets i called up the family and 
said please unpack those puppets and come to spoleto they were 
thrilled to come they are quaint they are like oldfashioned 
dolls they have that charm 
the colla marionettes were a hit at the charleston event in 
1987 this time menotti sought and got sponsorship from cocacola 
about the marriage of figaro the composerconductor said it 
was an opera of love 
all the music is sweet tenderness he said its nothing 
to do with politics the acidity of the beaumarchais play is 
nowhere to be felt at the end everybody is happy 
when he rehearses figaro menotti does the first scene to 
see what the singers can do then jumps to the fourth act 
everybody does the first and second act very well the third a 
little less and they dont direct the fourth act at all 
in my first rehearsals i dont say anything i want to see 
what they do instinctively some all you have to do is guide them 
i like to work with young people you get with stars sometimes you 
have trouble 
his figaro staging wont be eccentric menotti said i go 
straight to the score read what the librettist said see what the 
music tells me to do it may already have been done i dont care 
menotti is acclaimed as an opera director h took over the 
figaro when patrice chereau dropped out for a film commitment 
menotti had declared that hed stage only his own operas after the 
parsifal he directed last summer in trieste 
i love parsifal the opera is about compassion he said 
one thing is so clear in the score parsifal is epileptic 
everytime he talks about his mother he starts to tremble in the 
second act i make him faint he has a tremendous mother complex 
before freud 
the only thing i changed from wagner is the grail is taken 
away at the end parsifal takes the grail and goes out into the 
world for me the grail is the symbol of hope and peace 
otello is an opera in which the title character is usually 
directed as epileptic menotti believes otello suffers instead from 
jealousy youve never been jealous like i have been ive 
suffered jealousy so strong i could have killed 
menottis most recent opera is wedding day composed for the 
olympics in seoul last september and based on a korean legend 
i had chosen a cast in america of koreans he said i was 
only allowed to bring two of them i was in a theater where the 
curtain took a whole minute to go up or down the opera was in six 
scenes so 12 minutes was spent on the curtain 
menotti also ran into cultural problems in nearly every scene 
in the first he had two friends who hadnt seen each other for 
years meet and embrace 
they said they cant touch i had the music passionate and 
the people facing each other with praying hands he said 
in charleston jeanyves thibaudet will give a recital on 
opening night dedicating the festivals new steinway piano from 
germany besides figaro there also is bellinis la 
straniera which was last fully staged in the united states at a 
new york performance in 1834 
there also will be a play chamber music dance and jazz 
menotti is trying to raise money to build a theater near his 
home in scotland its so i wont have to travel around the 
world id like to have a theater outside my door so i can prepare 
my things there all i need is 1 million 
the composer of amahl and the night visitors said that one 
of several commissions he has is for a childrens opera for the 
atlanta symphony 
robert shaw atlanta director wants it for his farewell 
menotti said one is a trio for the chamber music society of 
lincoln center one is a piano concerto 
he also is starting a book to be titled memoirs and 
fantasies 
its going to be like swiss cheese full of holes what i 
cant remember ill make up he said 
but dont look for menotti to get even with anybody i 
think there is nothing worse than being vindictive its one thing 
i want to avoid 
